"{\"uid\": \"velo.outsideonline.com-olympics-olympic-bike-cost-paris-2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Powered byOutside Most athletes get to at the pro level ride whatever their sponsor has them ride.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 99, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most athletes\", \"from\": 18, \"to\": 31}, {\"ngram\": \"the pro level ride\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 60}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 61, \"to\": 69}, {\"ngram\": \"their sponsor\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 83}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More frequently still, the paint scheme is dictated by the team colorway.\", \"from\": 100, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the paint scheme\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 139}, {\"ngram\": \"the team colorway\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every four years though (or five in the case of 2021), we get to see a special colorway made especially for the2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"a special colorway\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes, the colors are made to represent the rider's home country.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the colors\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"the rider's home country\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other times, it's an opportunity for a manufacturer to strut their stuff with a limited edition bike.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"a manufacturer\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"strut\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"a limited edition bike\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in the case of one bike, it was even named after the Olympics (the Nishiki Olympic that's probably hanging up in your uncle's garage).\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"one bike\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"the Nishiki Olympic\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"your uncle's garage\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Below are some of our favorites that we have spotted, some we expect to see at the men's and women's Olympic road races, and how much a bike in the Olympics might cost.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our favorites\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's and women's Olympic road races\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Want one for yourself?\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canyon has been busy releasing its new Aeroad race bike, and the brand is commemorating its use in the Olympics with a special MACH874 paint theme.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Canyon\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"its new Aeroad race bike\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"its use\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"a special MACH874 paint theme\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The name comes from the Olympics being in Paris, sometimes called \\\"The City of Light.\\\"\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8387462963947935e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\"