dia.org/resource/Code_of_Federal_Regulations\", \"score\": 0.6474386192620842, \"rank\": 0.5411010112672279, \"text\": \"CFR\", \"types\": [\"Q737498\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Code_of_Federal_Regulations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Code_of_Federal_Regulations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Canyon\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"this specific Aeroad\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1513}, {\"ngram\": \"sale\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That makes it the least expensive race bike here.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is unless you count the Brompton!\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brompton_Bicycle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.257027693516418e-16, \"text\": \"Brompton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brompton_Bicycle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brompton_Bicycle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wout van Aert spent his time riding to his Olympic bronze medal in the men's time trial aboard the recently updated Cerv\\u00e9lo P5 time trial bike.And while the bike made waves for being set up with dual disc wheels front and rear, it also has a light blue flash on the fork.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wout van Aert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic bronze medal\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's ti